{
  "stem": "17044.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Even a button from our coats, we wouldn't give up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We'll fight.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we'll win.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And nobody believed that after two weeks, Poland was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] invaded and destroyed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the meantime, it was the Ribbentrop with Molotov agreement that a part of Poland, we will give to the Russians.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the front was-- it happened to be, this border is by our town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The Bug River is-- They call us, Western Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We belong to-- in what it was Eastern Poland, Western Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We'll give them to the Russian.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But the Germans, they came in to our town anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were scared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The Ukrainian farmers came with bags, sacks under their arms, to rob the stores.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because they knew the Germans don't like the Jews, and they'll give them a free hand.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans came in, and the opposite.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She-- they gave out orders, everybody will be punished.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anybody who will break into stores or to houses will be punished.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they let us know that this part, [BACKGROUND NOISE] we have agreement.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They are only temporary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In a couple days, that the Russian army will come in here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the same time, the farmers left back to their homes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the same time, there was a lot of communist people were waiting already for liberation with this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They went and to make a gates to receive the Russian army, and with the red flags, running with the bikes, with the horses, and everything.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So a group from Polish army, where they were escaping and-- and to the east, they find out that the Germans left town, they came in.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came back to our town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they started shooting.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
